text:
Reminder the *HubSpot CMS for Developers Exam Prep Session is tomorrow*. We will have a short window of time for Q&A. About ~10 minutes.

If you’d like to have a question answered regarding the developers certification, please submit through the form: <https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSe4PjCPVlRGrgo2WbZu_ByjwleMXui1UVHbmOvZuUZWjVgGCQ/viewform|Ask your questions here!>

If you’d like to attend, <https://events.HubSpot.com/events/details/HubSpot-HubSpot-academy-presents-HubSpot-cms-for-developers-certification-exam-prep/|register to attend>, It’s virtual. July 27th at 11 AM EDT.

:thank-you:  and good luck to everyone applying for CMS developer certification!
